WEBVTT

00:02:16.080 --> 00:02:19.199
So you killed Master Liu as well.

00:02:19.520 --> 00:02:21.199
And you pretended to be the female ghost in red.

00:02:22.000 --> 00:02:23.560
If it weren't for that fire...

00:02:23.560 --> 00:02:25.520
...that spread to Master Liu's room with the wind...

00:02:25.919 --> 00:02:27.240
...and everyone rushed to put it out...

00:02:27.919 --> 00:02:30.120
...did you intend to kill Ding Da right then?

00:02:30.520 --> 00:02:31.800
And destroy the body and the evidence together?

00:02:32.680 --> 00:02:34.080
It's death either way.

00:02:34.840 --> 00:02:36.120
It doesn't matter how they die.

00:02:36.840 --> 00:02:39.400
Then how did you fool everyone and impersonate Xu Qingqing?

00:02:39.800 --> 00:02:41.199
Even if the others didn't know her...

00:02:41.680 --> 00:02:43.919
...Xiao Bai is the Young Lord's personal maid.

00:02:44.439 --> 00:02:45.520
Surely she would recognize her.

00:02:46.639 --> 00:02:47.639
Because...

00:02:47.639 --> 00:02:50.159
...I look somewhat like Xu Qingqing.

00:02:51.319 --> 00:02:52.639
So later on...

00:02:52.639 --> 00:02:55.319
...the Manor Lord occasionally ordered me to impersonate her.

00:02:55.319 --> 00:02:56.560
As for Xiao Bai...

00:02:57.280 --> 00:02:58.719
...she's called a personal maid...

00:02:59.280 --> 00:03:01.000
...but she only prepared food.

00:03:01.479 --> 00:03:02.800
She didn't serve her personally.

00:03:03.560 --> 00:03:05.159
Naturally, she couldn't tell.

00:03:05.240 --> 00:03:05.759
Why?

00:03:06.759 --> 00:03:08.560
Because the real Xu Qingqing...

00:03:08.800 --> 00:03:10.120
...has been simple-minded since childhood.

00:03:10.719 --> 00:03:13.840
She was said to be ill and never saw anyone.

00:03:14.560 --> 00:03:15.719
After Madam passed away...

00:03:16.240 --> 00:03:18.840
...the Manor Lord forbade her from leaving her room even more.

00:03:19.439 --> 00:03:21.199
And didn't allow others to approach her.

00:03:22.319 --> 00:03:23.960
The Young Lord that outsiders saw...

00:03:24.319 --> 00:03:27.120
...was always me in disguise.

00:03:34.919 --> 00:03:35.719
Father.

00:03:51.080 --> 00:03:52.000
Say it again.

00:03:54.800 --> 00:03:55.639
Father.

00:04:00.080 --> 00:04:00.840
Good.

00:04:03.639 --> 00:04:04.960
After killing the Manor Lord...

00:04:06.280 --> 00:04:08.280
...I became the real Xu Qingqing.

00:04:10.520 --> 00:04:12.000
I called Xiao Bai into the room.

00:04:12.879 --> 00:04:14.039
The first time she saw me...

00:04:14.680 --> 00:04:15.560
...she was convinced...

00:04:16.040 --> 00:04:18.240
...that I was the Young Lord she had served for years.

00:04:18.959 --> 00:04:20.040
She didn't doubt it at all.

00:04:20.399 --> 00:04:21.680
If it weren't for you two...

00:04:22.319 --> 00:04:23.720
...I would have succeeded long ago.

00:04:24.439 --> 00:04:25.920
Then where is the Manor Lord's real daughter?

00:04:26.199 --> 00:04:27.759
I went to her room to impersonate her...

00:04:28.560 --> 00:04:29.439
...and I wanted to save her too.

00:04:30.040 --> 00:04:31.399
But she wasn't there.

00:04:32.639 --> 00:04:36.439
Perhaps the Manor Lord locked her up somewhere else.

00:04:37.120 --> 00:04:38.399
You didn't lock her up?

00:04:38.720 --> 00:04:40.279
My brother died a miserable, innocent death.

00:04:41.199 --> 00:04:43.079
How could I harm another innocent person?

00:04:46.560 --> 00:04:48.000
Then where would the Manor Lord hide her?

00:04:51.600 --> 00:04:54.120
A cave or a secret chamber, perhaps.

00:04:55.000 --> 00:04:56.040
I don't know.

00:04:57.199 --> 00:04:58.399
The Manor is so big.

00:04:59.439 --> 00:05:02.000
It's too easy to hide someone.

00:05:03.120 --> 00:05:05.040
But even if his daughter is simple-minded...

00:05:05.519 --> 00:05:07.319
...why would the Manor Lord treat her this way?

00:05:09.560 --> 00:05:13.040
Because she isn't his biological daughter.

00:05:17.120 --> 00:05:18.959
This was a scandal of the Manor.

00:05:19.639 --> 00:05:21.439
The Old Manor Lord recruited a live-in son-in-law...

00:05:21.879 --> 00:05:23.519
...merely to cover up the shame.

00:05:25.040 --> 00:05:26.279
Otherwise...

00:05:26.680 --> 00:05:29.279
...it wouldn't be the turn of this despicable bookkeeper.

00:05:31.519 --> 00:05:33.319
He pretended to dote on the Young Lord...

00:05:33.319 --> 00:05:34.399
...and dote on Madam.

00:05:35.240 --> 00:05:38.000
It was just to gain the Old Manor Lord and Madam's trust...

00:05:39.680 --> 00:05:42.160
...so they would feel safe handing the Manor over to him.

00:05:43.079 --> 00:05:44.040
A man who loves his wife...

00:05:44.319 --> 00:05:46.120
...how could he let her favorite Lotus Garden fall into ruin?

00:05:48.079 --> 00:05:49.360
If he didn't want to be reminded of her...

00:05:49.360 --> 00:05:50.399
...he could just not go there.

00:05:56.560 --> 00:05:58.639
Vengeance is complete.

00:05:59.040 --> 00:06:01.879
I have no regrets.

00:06:05.360 --> 00:06:06.399
Xiao Bai.

00:06:09.399 --> 00:06:11.000
I'm sorry.

00:06:12.480 --> 00:06:13.800
Brilliant.

00:06:14.560 --> 00:06:16.480
Truly brilliant.

00:06:20.240 --> 00:06:20.920
Quick!

00:06:25.240 --> 00:06:26.000
The Secret Inspectorate!

00:06:26.600 --> 00:06:28.079
Aren't they serving Lord Nine Thousand Years in the palace?

00:06:28.199 --> 00:06:29.040
What are they doing here?

00:06:31.240 --> 00:06:32.800
You'll have to ask Lord Nine Thousand Years.

00:06:35.839 --> 00:06:36.759
Lord Nine Thousand Years...

00:06:37.079 --> 00:06:39.120
...falsely accused my father of treason...

00:06:39.959 --> 00:06:42.000
...and killed my whole family.

00:06:45.879 --> 00:06:47.279
Ye Li.

00:06:48.160 --> 00:06:49.000
I'll take you away.

00:06:56.639 --> 00:06:57.319
Don't be afraid, Zhao Yun.

00:06:57.319 --> 00:06:59.040
Kill. Leave no one alive.

00:06:59.079 --> 00:06:59.680
Yes!

00:07:13.959 --> 00:07:14.480
My Lord

00:07:16.800 --> 00:07:17.560
Liu Shiwu

00:07:21.439 --> 00:07:22.439
Young Lord

00:07:23.800 --> 00:07:24.399
No

00:07:25.639 --> 00:07:28.519
I should call you Miss Huang Cui now

00:07:30.439 --> 00:07:32.240
I was just outside

00:07:32.240 --> 00:07:33.959
I've been listening for quite a while

00:07:34.199 --> 00:07:36.000
But I haven't heard the main point

00:07:36.759 --> 00:07:39.519
So I decided to come ask you face-to-face

00:07:40.839 --> 00:07:42.839
This setup of the All-Knowing Night Banquet...

00:07:43.920 --> 00:07:45.199
...was your doing?

00:07:47.399 --> 00:07:48.000
Yes

00:07:48.600 --> 00:07:50.160
You did it alone?

00:07:52.279 --> 00:07:53.040
Yes

00:07:53.879 --> 00:07:54.560
Good

00:07:55.759 --> 00:07:59.120
Since you were able to lure everyone into this trap...

00:07:59.839 --> 00:08:02.959
...you must also know the secret behind it

00:08:03.439 --> 00:08:04.399
I don't know

00:08:06.000 --> 00:08:07.399
Although I have followed the Manor Lord for years...

00:08:08.399 --> 00:08:11.720
...I only know the Thousand-Mechanism Treasure of the Manor...

00:08:12.000 --> 00:08:13.519
...can grant one the world

00:08:13.879 --> 00:08:14.959
Using it as bait...

00:08:16.120 --> 00:08:19.120
...was merely to make the culprit walk right into the trap

00:08:21.600 --> 00:08:22.920
Still stubborn

00:08:25.920 --> 00:08:26.439
Torture her

00:08:26.439 --> 00:08:26.839
Yes

00:08:26.839 --> 00:08:28.199
Beat her until she speaks

00:08:28.199 --> 00:08:29.600
She is a key criminal of the Dali Temple

00:08:30.079 --> 00:08:31.120
I'd like to see who dares to touch her

00:08:34.759 --> 00:08:35.279
Master Kun

00:08:36.320 --> 00:08:37.000
Arrest them

00:08:39.919 --> 00:08:41.279
Move! No! No!

00:08:43.559 --> 00:08:44.799
The people of the All-Knowing Manor...

00:08:45.080 --> 00:08:46.399
...intended to commit treason

00:08:46.720 --> 00:08:49.399
The Secret Inspectorate orders your immediate detention

00:08:49.480 --> 00:08:50.080
Detain them!

00:08:51.799 --> 00:08:52.639
Don't fight head-on

00:09:02.879 --> 00:09:03.960
Quick, sit down

00:09:06.960 --> 00:09:07.679
Let me see

00:09:10.639 --> 00:09:11.039
Bless us

00:09:11.120 --> 00:09:11.519
Let me do it

00:09:12.320 --> 00:09:12.919
Let me see

00:09:14.360 --> 00:09:16.000
Bless us. Bless us, bless us

00:09:16.000 --> 00:09:17.600
Bodhisattva bless us

00:09:18.080 --> 00:09:18.879
Bodhisattva bless us

00:09:20.480 --> 00:09:21.279
Bodhisattva bless us

00:09:22.200 --> 00:09:23.159
This isn't working

00:09:23.720 --> 00:09:24.919
I need to get the hemostatic powder

00:09:25.159 --> 00:09:26.039
You watch over him here

00:09:26.120 --> 00:09:26.960
I'll be right back

00:09:28.000 --> 00:09:28.679
Okay

00:09:37.440 --> 00:09:39.039
Where are you going?

00:09:41.799 --> 00:09:42.559
My Lord...

00:09:43.240 --> 00:09:44.639
Lord Hua won't stop bleeding

00:09:45.320 --> 00:09:47.120
I want to go to the pharmacy to get some medicine

00:09:49.159 --> 00:09:50.480
He does need medicine applied

00:09:51.320 --> 00:09:54.559
Can't let His Majesty think I harm my colleagues

00:09:55.200 --> 00:09:57.399
If Lord Nine Thousand Years is implicated...

00:09:57.759 --> 00:09:59.879
...my sin would be great indeed

00:10:01.039 --> 00:10:01.519
Go ahead

00:10:09.039 --> 00:10:11.039
Beat her until she speaks

00:10:16.559 --> 00:10:17.559
Master Ye

00:10:21.000 --> 00:10:21.639
Could we...

00:10:22.039 --> 00:10:23.279
...speak in private?

00:10:26.559 --> 00:10:27.279
Don't go

00:10:28.480 --> 00:10:29.720
They have bad intentions

00:10:30.679 --> 00:10:31.360
Don't worry

00:10:32.240 --> 00:10:33.440
He won't do anything to me

00:10:35.960 --> 00:10:36.559
Ye Li

00:10:37.200 --> 00:10:37.799
Ye Li

00:10:58.639 --> 00:10:59.320
Close the door.

00:11:04.759 --> 00:11:05.519
I know.

00:11:06.759 --> 00:11:08.279
You all have plenty of tricks.

00:11:09.159 --> 00:11:11.440
But since you're all locked up,

00:11:11.759 --> 00:11:13.320
I advise you all to behave.

00:11:17.200 --> 00:11:18.320
Bullying a girl

00:11:19.080 --> 00:11:20.240
won't help you solve the riddle.

00:11:21.240 --> 00:11:23.919
So you're saying you have a lead?

00:11:25.720 --> 00:11:26.360
About that riddle.

00:11:26.639 --> 00:11:29.960
Because the Metropolitan Governor refused to retry the old Chaoheng case,

00:11:31.360 --> 00:11:32.960
you killed him.

00:11:36.159 --> 00:11:37.320
So that is what you wanted to ask, My Lord.

00:11:38.120 --> 00:11:39.440
Not just that.

00:11:40.919 --> 00:11:41.919
Please see the truth, My Lord.

00:11:42.200 --> 00:11:44.080
I didn't even see Lord Meng that day.

00:11:44.639 --> 00:11:45.919
He realized he was being followed,

00:11:46.320 --> 00:11:47.840
so he asked me to investigate.

00:11:48.440 --> 00:11:49.519
When I arrived,

00:11:49.799 --> 00:11:50.799
he was still meeting a guest.

00:11:51.120 --> 00:11:53.600
I thought I'd drink a cup of tea and wait for him.

00:11:54.279 --> 00:11:55.360
And guess what happened?

00:11:55.919 --> 00:11:56.840
After I finished that tea,

00:11:56.840 --> 00:11:57.879
I passed out.

00:11:59.120 --> 00:12:02.519
So you're saying you were framed.

00:12:03.159 --> 00:12:04.399
Exactly.

00:12:05.080 --> 00:12:08.600
So you volunteered to come to the Manor to investigate,

00:12:09.639 --> 00:12:11.000
in order to protect yourself.

00:12:11.679 --> 00:12:12.720
Why else?

00:12:12.919 --> 00:12:14.440
Who wants to die if they can live?

00:12:16.759 --> 00:12:17.480
My Lord,

00:12:17.639 --> 00:12:20.200
do you know that the blade that day...

00:12:20.200 --> 00:12:21.600
...was held right here?

00:12:21.600 --> 00:12:22.120
Here.

00:12:22.480 --> 00:12:23.799
I was this close to...

00:12:26.720 --> 00:12:29.039
Then you already know the solution to the Treasure?

00:12:29.879 --> 00:12:31.399
I... don't know.

00:12:32.559 --> 00:12:33.080
My Lord,

00:12:33.480 --> 00:12:35.759
is there a connection between these two questions?

00:12:35.960 --> 00:12:37.039
Master Ye,

00:12:38.039 --> 00:12:39.679
you went to the Metropolitan Governor's estate,

00:12:39.799 --> 00:12:41.080
and Lord Meng died.

00:12:41.519 --> 00:12:42.840
You came to this Manor,

00:12:42.960 --> 00:12:44.120
and the Manor Lord died.

00:12:44.240 --> 00:12:45.840
The guests died too.

00:12:46.679 --> 00:12:47.679
Master Ye,

00:12:48.320 --> 00:12:50.200
you are a bad omen.

00:12:50.879 --> 00:12:51.440
Perhaps,

00:12:52.519 --> 00:12:53.799
it is not that I am ominous,

00:12:54.559 --> 00:12:56.159
but that the Heavens have opened their eyes,

00:12:57.720 --> 00:12:59.360
borrowing my righteousness

00:12:59.759 --> 00:13:01.320
to rid the people of evil.